PN,40801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,FA stepmother killed a five-year-old
OL,7,Fgirl by scalding her in a hot bath as
OL,8,Fa punishment nearly half a century
OL,9,Fago, jurors found.
OL,11,FJanice Nix, 67, was found guilty of
OL,12,Fthe manslaughter of Andrea Bernard by
OL,13,Fforcing her into the bath in Thornton
OL,14,FHeath, south London, in 1978.
OL,16,FAndrea's death was treated as an
OL,17,Faccident until her older brother
OL,18,FDesmond Bernard went to police in 2022
OL,19,Fwith a new account of what happened,
OL,20,FIsleworth Crown Court heard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
