OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,FNix, of Clapham, south London, shook
OL,7,Fher head before weeping in the dock as
OL,8,Fshe was also convicted of cruelty to
OL,9,FMr Bernard between October 1975 and
OL,10,FJune 1978, when he was seven to nine-
OL,11,Fyears-old.
OL,13,FShe could be seen crying hysterically
OL,14,Fin the dock after jurors left the
OL,15,Fcourtroom.
OL,17,FGiving evidence during the trial, Mr
OL,18,FBernard, now 56, tearfully told jurors
OL,19,Fthat he had initially described his
OL,20,Fsister's death as an accident because
OL,21,Fhe wanted Nix to stop beating him.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
