OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,FMr Bernard said that Nix beat him with
OL,7,Fa belt, burned him with a cigarette,
OL,8,Fbit him and made him eat cat food.
OL,10,FHe said that Nix regularly beat the
OL,11,Fchildren, even for not folding their
OL,12,Fclothes "to her standards".
OL,14,FMr Bernard described Nix as physically
OL,15,F"strong" with a "heavy-set build".
OL,17,FJurors heard that on June 6 1978, Nix
OL,18,Fwas "furious" after Andrea ignored
OL,19,Finstructions not to leave the house
OL,20,Fand to help clean instead.
