OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,FNix shouted at Andrea in an "extremely
OL,7,Floud" voice before beating her, the
OL,8,Fcourt heard.
OL,10,FMr Bernard said he later heard the
OL,11,Fbath running.
OL,13,FHe went on: "I could hear Janice
OL,14,Fshouting 'get in the bath' and I could
OL,15,Fhear Andrea saying 'the bath is too
OL,16,Fhot mummy'.
OL,18,F"I could hear Janice shouting 'get in
OL,19,Fthe bath, get in the bath' and then I
OL,20,Fheard screaming and splashing.
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@EO]uD@MOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,F"Then I heard the screaming stopped
OL,7,Fand I could hear Janice calling Andrea
OL,8,Fto 'wake up, wake up'."
OL,10,FAsked by prosecutor Kerry Broome how
OL,11,FNix sounded, he replied: "She sounded
OL,12,Fscared."
OL,14,FMr Bernard said he then entered the
OL,15,Fbathroom and saw Nix cradling Andrea,
OL,16,Fwho was "limp" and wrapped in a towel.
OL,18,FHe added: "I could see skin falling
OL,19,Foff her."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@WO]sD@ZOUtD@HO]xD@IOUxD@NO]zD@
OL,26,AKOU{D@IO]
