OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,FHe told jurors he lived in "constant
OL,7,Ffear" of Nix's beatings and did not
OL,8,Ftell anyone because he feared being
OL,9,F"punished more".
OL,11,FSpeaking about why he decided to tell
OL,12,Fothers about his sister's death, Mr
OL,13,FBernard said: "I couldn't carry on
OL,14,Fdealing with it, so that's what I did."
OL,16,FHe added: "To place this burden where
OL,17,Fit should go."
OL,19,FAndrea died nearly six weeks after
OL,20,Farriving at hospital with burns to 50%
OL,21,Fof her body, the court heard.
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@EO]qD@AOUqD@OO]uD@OOUvD@gO]xD@
OL,26,AKOUyD@NO]
