PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,FA burns expert told the trial that a
OL,7,Fchild exposed to water hot enough to
OL,8,Fcause Andrea's injuries would
OL,9,Finstinctively try to get out by
OL,10,Fstanding up, not remain seated.
OL,12,FProsecutors argued this meant Nix must
OL,13,Fhave forcibly held parts of Andrea's
OL,14,Fbody underwater.
OL,16,FNix, then called Janice Thomas and in
OL,17,Fher late teenage years, had been in a
OL,18,Frelationship with the children's
OL,19,Ffather, also named Desmond Bernard,
OL,20,Fand was in effect their stepmother,
OL,21,Fthe court heard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
