OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,FDuring the 1978 inquest investigation,
OL,7,FNix had initially claimed Andrea took
OL,8,Fa bath on her own and later complained
OL,9,Fof itchy legs before fainting, jurors
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FBut she admitted during her trial to
OL,13,Fgiving a false account of the events
OL,14,Fto the coroner because she was "in a
OL,15,Fpanic" over having failed to supervise
OL,16,FAndrea while she took a bath.
OL,18,F"I realised I had done something I
OL,19,Fshouldn't have done: I should have
OL,20,Fbeen with Andrea," she told jurors.
OL,26,@vD@`OUwD@FO]zD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
