OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,F"I was young and I was clearly not
OL,7,Fthinking. On hindsight now, I see my
OL,8,Fnegligence as a teenager."
OL,10,FThe defendant further told the court
OL,11,Fshe did not at the time realise the
OL,12,Fbathwater was scalding hot, adding:
OL,13,F"All I know is that she was in
OL,14,Fdistress, her legs were red, they had
OL,15,Fbubbles on them... I didn't know how
OL,16,Fhot the water was."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@ZO]uD@AOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/16
