FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,FDuring a 2022 police interview, Nix
OL,7,Fgave a version of events that differed
OL,8,F"significantly" from her original
OL,9,Fstatement from the time, having not
OL,10,Fbeen told that investigators had found
OL,11,Fit, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,13,FShe also claimed that the coroner
OL,14,Ffound Andrea's death was because of an
OL,15,Foverheated bath caused by a faulty
OL,16,Fboiler ` something not mentioned in
OL,17,Fthe report.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
