OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,FNix was arrested at Heathrow Airport
OL,7,Fon February 18, 2025, after arriving
OL,8,Fon a flight from Antigua, and was
OL,9,Fcharged later that day.
OL,11,FNix had denied both the charges of
OL,12,Fmanslaughter and cruelty to a child.
OL,14,FDetective inspector Louise Caveen,
OL,15,Ffrom the Met's cold case homicide
OL,16,Fteam, said: "This is a particularly
OL,17,Ftragic case and my thoughts ultimately
OL,18,Fremain with Andrea's family, whose
OL,19,Flives were changed irrevocably back in
OL,20,F1978.
OL,26,@xD@MOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,F"In particular, I want to pay tribute
OL,7,Fto Desmond, who bravely made the
OL,8,Fdecision to come forward and speak to
OL,9,Fus, as well as giving evidence at
OL,10,Ftrial.
OL,12,F"It is thanks to his courage that Nix
OL,13,Fhas now been found guilty and will
OL,14,Ffinally be held responsible for her
OL,15,Factions."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/16
