PN,40814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,FAisling Hosein of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service said: "This was a
OL,8,Fharrowing case where Janice Nix
OL,9,Fsubjected Andrea and her older brother
OL,10,Fto a sustained period of abuse,
OL,11,Fculminating in the tragic death of a
OL,12,Ffive-year-old girl after she was
OL,13,Fforced into a scalding hot bath.
OL,15,F"This prosecution only came about
OL,16,Fafter Andrea's brother reported his
OL,17,Fstepmother's actions to police in
OL,18,FSeptember 2022, resulting in the
OL,19,Fcircumstances into what happened on
OL,20,Fthat day in 1978 being re-examined.
OL,26,@oD@[OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780052575
OL,3,CStepmother killed girl in scalding
OL,4,Cbath in 1978, jury finds
OL,6,F"I can only imagine the enormous
OL,7,Fcourage this must have taken to come
OL,8,Fforward after being told as a child to
OL,9,Fsay the incident was just an accident.
OL,11,F"It is thanks to him that we have been
OL,12,Fable to secure justice today on behalf
OL,13,Fof Andrea almost five decades on."
OL,15,FNix was remanded in custody to be
OL,16,Fsentenced at a later date.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@bO]
